===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|now|chiefly|US}} A member (especially a senior one) of the faculty at a [[college]] or [[university]]; an [[academic]]. {{defdate|from 17th c.}}
# A member or follower of an [[academy]], or society for [[promoting]] science, art, or literature, such as the [[French Academy]], or the Royal Academy of Arts. {{defdate|from 17th c.}}
#* '''1890''', {{w|Oscar Wilde}}, ''The Picture of Dorian Gray'', Vintage 2007, page 9:
#*: ‘Well, after I had been in the room about ten minutes, talking to huge overdressed dowagers and tedious '''Academicians''', I suddenly became conscious that some one was looking at me.’

